high_descs: Walk to the cardboard box on your right.
Pick up the open box from the floor.
Turn around and walk to your left and then to the right and to the coffee table on your right.
Set the open box down on the coffee table.
Turn away from the coffee table and walk to the television on your right.
Pick up the television remote from the TV stand.
Turn back around to the coffee table.
Set the television remote down in the open box and then close the box.
anns.task_desc: Package up the television remote in a cardboard box on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn right and look down at the ground
Grab the cardboard box off of the ground
Turn around and go to the coffee table
Put the box on the table
Turn around and go to the TV stand
Grab the remote off of the stand
Turn around and go to the coffee table
Put the remote in the box on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting a remote in a cardboard box on the coffee table

high_descs: Turn right then face the box in front of you.
Take the box in front of you.
Turn right, then right and face the center table on your right.
Place the box on the table in front of you.
Turn around and face the tv in front of you.
Take the remote from the tv stand in front of you.
Turn around and face the center table in front of you.
Place the remote in the box on the table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place the remote in a box on a table.
